{"tid":486272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個英迷 咁既分組真係得啖笑","createTime":"2017-12-01T16:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T03:32:43.000Z","uid":69180,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93820ae258727451d9cc7f28c4bc1b95e4a481f1","tid":486272,"uid":69180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"作為一個英迷 咁既分組真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈英格蘭首名有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班英迷 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先比利時,唔好玩啦 歐洲二線野，3分穩陣<br />\n<br />\n巴拿馬,,如果係巴西狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..英半力夠WIN,又3分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又3分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 簡尼，華迪， 阿里，拉舒福特加上關鍵王史達寧.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n9分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手英格蘭..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"28fe2f4fc2961d459f68c3384f893b14c65c7ec7","tid":486272,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e17a696d485d4416e8029215096e62fea60903","tid":486272,"uid":121066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"名都唔記得個隊真係要load一load先記得"},{"pid":"0af3495f17a8d507d4b4fbb36b81a0925a71fbb2","tid":486272,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"關鍵王史達寧，呢句真"},{"pid":"26168dd69bfd9e7e8403313dc8d3e51d3f935a5d","tid":486272,"uid":69180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關鍵王史達寧，呢句真</blockquote><br />\n世界杯已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f426f83c95352b43122afb509e54ec3a530ad59","tid":486272,"uid":62343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關鍵王史達寧，呢句真</blockquote><br />\n世界杯已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n守85分鐘等丁爆seed is ok"},{"pid":"83